flowchart TD
    A[User Receives New Message] --> B{Check Notification Settings}
    B -->|Enabled| C[Send Push Notification]
    B -->|Disabled| D[Do Not Send Notification]
    C --> E{Notification Type}
    E -->|Chat| F[Send Chat Notification]
    E -->|System| G[Send System Notification]
    E -->|Promotional| H[Send Promotional Notification]
    F --> I[User Clicks Notification]
    G --> I
    H --> I
    I --> J[Open Chat or App]
    J --> K{User Notification Controls}
    K -->|Per-Chat Settings| L[Adjust Notification for Specific Chat]
    K -->|Global Settings| M[Adjust Global Notification Preferences]
    L --> N[Save Changes]
    M --> N
    N --> O[Update Notification Preferences]